{"tid":576400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"M記廢老買早餐食一事有感","createTime":"2018-03-01T01:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T01:39:05.000Z","uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"baee8d197e74aec6c8a5a4086a193a3414e568f4","tid":576400,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"今日十點堂，又早咗起身，一於去M記食個早餐。買完個餐，搵個位，戴上耳機，睇吓劏房波有咩理財新哲學。<br />\n<br />\n食食下，忽然聽到D老嘢爭執嘅聲，心諗：「啲廢老又做乜鳩，咩雅興都冇曬。」除低耳機，回頭一睇，原來係有個啊婆係個位度嘈：「我要1號餐，1號餐啊，就冇架啦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n個M記啊蟬好粗魯咁講：「<span style=\"color: red;\">你地</span>坐低先啦，一陣先幫你地去收銀度幫你地買啦！」無錯！係你地，基本上啲老人家照照早都圍埋一齊傾計坐到2046。以佢地對話嘅口吻，應該唔係第一次要求店員幫佢地落order，應該係習以為常。<br />\n<br />\n我繼續食我嘅早餐，睇facebook live。一路係度諗，究竟係咪個店員縱壞晒佢地呢？但係講真，唔係每個店員都做得到，呢個唔係佢職責所在，大可以唔理會走咗去。雖然言語上態度唔太好，但係行為上其實都愛惜老人家。<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔，你地覺得個店員幫老人家買餐呢個行為啱唔啱呢？<br />\n<br />\n店員冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n縱壞曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f692f38c2a764cd31543f77fcf53ab4cc6c211","tid":576400,"uid":192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"你請佢地食幾十件薯餅啦<br />\n第二日就唔洗見到佢地"},{"pid":"2de7dfa41a11886548c808c9f0a68071c3317e54","tid":576400,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f692f38c2a764cd31543f77fcf53ab4cc6c211","tid":576400,"uid":192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"你請佢地食幾十件薯餅啦<br />\n第二日就唔洗見到佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:08:20.000Z","msg":"窮J大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbcbfb89e9e7bba0063b9e58e6b5995ab852e71","tid":576400,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2de7dfa41a11886548c808c9f0a68071c3317e54","tid":576400,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f692f38c2a764cd31543f77fcf53ab4cc6c211","tid":576400,"uid":192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"你請佢地食幾十件薯餅啦<br />\n第二日就唔洗見到佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:08:20.000Z","msg":"窮J大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:11:03.000Z","msg":"試下買一個餐，溝老鼠藥<br />\n<br />\n放係到唔食走人，幾大機會比人執去食"},{"pid":"7640b197948aba93a42ba466906d1967fa2539c1","tid":576400,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28df74358a4c81d1f8c564ee9cf2bc0c871de2f1","tid":576400,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecee4f3222c0dcbc77bb9d5aa4d81e0beb52fe3","tid":576400,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}